<div id="main-article" class="article-content retro-folders">
<p>Batman is awesome enough to warrant his own <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/SugarWiki/MomentOfAwesome" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/SugarWiki/MomentOfAwesome">Moment of Awesome</a> section. Because he's the <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/AllStarBatmanAndRobinTheBoyWonder" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/ComicBook/AllStarBatmanAndRobinTheBoyWonder">goddamn Batman</a>.</p><p></p><div class="folderlabel" onclick="toggleAllFolders();">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;open/close all folders&nbsp; </div><div class="folderlabel" onclick="togglefolder('folder0');">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Comic Books&nbsp;</div><div id="folder0" class="folder" isfolder="true" style="display:block;"><span class="asscaps">Ongoing Series</span><p></p><ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/SupermanBatman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/SupermanBatman">Superman/Batman</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/GrantMorrisonsBatman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/GrantMorrisonsBatman">Grant Morrison's Batman</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/TheBatmanAdventures" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/TheBatmanAdventures">The Batman Adventures</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/Batgirl2011" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/Batgirl2011">Batgirl (2011)</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/RedHoodAndTheOutlaws" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/RedHoodAndTheOutlaws">Red Hood and the Outlaws</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/Batwoman" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/Batwoman">Batwoman</a></em></li></ul><p><span class="asscaps">Comic Storylines</span></p><ul><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/BatmanYearOne" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Awesome/BatmanYearOne">Batman: Year One</a></em></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki